# Aviatrix Discovery

Aviatrix discovery is a complimentary set of scripts to [Aviatrix Migration](https://pypi.org/project/aviatrix-migration) scripts. Discovery Generator can automatically discover VPCs and generate input files for use with [Aviatrix Migration's](https://pypi.org/project/aviatrix-migration) network discovery, --stage_vpcs and --switch_traffic functions.

## Installation
Install via pip:
```
pip install aviatrix-discovery
```
Upgrade via pip:
```
pip install --upgrade aviatrix-discovery
```

## Discovering VPCs and/or VNETs

The migration process requires Aviatrix Advanced Services team help. Please contact Aviatrix for help with your discovery and migration project.
